1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što sam rekao na početku ove Svete mise, započeli smo jedno novo liturgijsko razdoblje.

2
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus danas u evanđelju kaže: "Tko hoće slijediti me, neka ostavi sve i neka ide sa mnom."

3
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko puta krećemo za Isusom?

4
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko puta smo odlučili, evo možda i ovoj korizmi, neću raditi ovo, činit ću ovu žrtvu, napravit ću ovo, odreknut ću se ovoga, izbacit ću ovo iz svog života.

5
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] I neke su stvari zaista dobre, čak neke inicijative vrlo pohvalne. Ja kad čujem od vas mladih, evo, moji dečki iz tehničke većine odlučilo svaki dan iću na misu.

6
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka čast. Vi mladi koji dolazite na mise, vrlo ste odlučni. Vrlo donosite ozbiljne odluke. Ja vas zato hvalim.

7
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvalim i one koji ne razumiju što rade. Jedno pitanje nam se postavlja svima večeras. Sve to što radite, sve to što ste donijeli odluke, ne samo u korizmi, nego u općenito u životu, je li pročišćava našu ljubav, našu motivaciju prema Bogu?

8
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ćete vjerovati da je to najbitnije.

9
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:58,739
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo paralelno raditi neke stvari. Odricati se, činiti, biti nazdočni u crkvi, ali da mi uopće duhovno ne rastemo, ne mijenjamo se. Ništa naša ljubav se ne mijenja.

10
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:18,439
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je fascinantno ko svećeniku kad slušam, evo ponekada ispovijedam, ljudi koji su u godinama, ljudi koji su godinama u crkvi, ljudi koji su prošli stotine korizmi iza sebe, nikakve oni promjene u svojoj ljubavi prema Bogu nemaju.

11
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isto čine žrtve. Isto donose odluke svake korizme svakog adventa.

12
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nešto fali. Zašto to Isus kaže tako danas u evanđelju?

13
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:37,939
[SPEAKER_00] Tko hoće ići za mno, neka se odrekne sebe samoga.

14
00:02:37,939 --> 00:02:46,419
[SPEAKER_00] Puno je lakše odrese slatkoga, alkohola, cigareta, nego sebe samoga.

15
00:02:48,000 --> 00:03:01,919
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto? Zašto Isus danas počinje križe, govori što će se sve njemu dogoditi, da mora propatiti, da umrijeti ovako i onako i onda kaže, ako hoćete slijedite me.

16
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] Da li vi svačate da u onom vremenu križ, umrijeti na križu, je bilo sramota, bilo proklestvo, bilo nešto najgora kazna.

17
00:03:16,819 --> 00:03:23,919
[SPEAKER_00] I sad on govori da će umrijeti tako i kaže, ako hoćete slijedite me.

18
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:26,139
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ko bi krenuo?

19
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto danas, i uče smo počeli korizmu, neće svi kršćani krenuti ozbiljno u neku pripremu za Isusom.

20
00:03:36,460 --> 00:03:38,120
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

21
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:45,120
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što isto koji židovi onoga vremena, ne vide u križu ništa više osim patnije.

22
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, Isus razmišlja drugačije.

23
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] Neće niko uskrsnuti tko nije prošao križ.

24
00:03:55,259 --> 00:04:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] To je mnogi nevjernici danas, ili oni mlaki kršćani, ne vide u križu nikakvog smisla.

25
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:11,680
[SPEAKER_00] Jer što ćeš da slijedim tebe, još da moram patit, trpi zbog tebe, bit progonjen, jer to je Isusovo obećanje.

26
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može biti učenik iznad učitelja.

27
00:04:15,460 --> 00:04:21,459
[SPEAKER_00] Ali uvijek mi svi promakne nam iz vidika uskrsnuća.

28
00:04:21,459 --> 00:04:31,160
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, ako u današnjem evanđelju Isus kaže, tko hoće ići za mno, neka uzme svoj križ i slijedi me.

29
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo i logiku džavla, koji nudi male zemajske stvari i sredstva u ovome svijetu da nas dobije.

30
00:04:45,699 --> 00:04:54,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ste pozorno slušali prvo čitanje, kaže sloboda, stari zavijet, još pričamo o starom zavijetu.

31
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:58,480
[SPEAKER_00] Pre tebe danas stavljam život ili smrt, biraj.

32
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:05,379
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto što nam je Bog dao kaj najljepši dar je sloboda, biraj.

33
00:05:05,379 --> 00:05:15,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ima ljudi koji su odabrali ovaj svjetovni život, materialni, slatke zadovoljštine i strasti,

34
00:05:15,699 --> 00:05:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] idu tim putem.

35
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:26,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako mi uzemo križ i svaćamo njegovu poruku, nešto se događa.

36
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] Da onaj koji uzme u slobodi i zabere Isusa i križ,

37
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:41,720
[SPEAKER_00] on već ovdje na zemlji, čak i kroz patnju, može doživjeti predukus neba.

38
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] Predokus uskrsnuća.

39
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:50,439
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, dao Bog slobodu, i zabereš li ovaj svijet,

40
00:05:50,439 --> 00:05:55,540
[SPEAKER_00] materialne stvari i sve ovo drugo što on nudi,

41
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:58,240
[SPEAKER_00] i džavo ima svoje obećanje,

42
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:01,120
[SPEAKER_00] proćeš kroz pakao,

43
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] jer nagrada ti je smrt.

44
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:14,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je žalosno što možda nekad osuđujemo grešnike.

45
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:20,620
[SPEAKER_00] Isus mrzi grijeh nikada grešnike.

46
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ne možete ni razumijeti kako je jedan grešnik pati.

47
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:32,959
[SPEAKER_00] I svako kad je u grijehu u službi Satone, pati jako.

48
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:38,740
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ne osjeća predokus neba, ne osjeća ljubav Božju,

49
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:41,899
[SPEAKER_00] i vlastiti grijeh te ubija.

50
00:06:41,899 --> 00:06:44,459
[SPEAKER_00] Ubija tvoju savjest.

51
00:06:44,459 --> 00:06:49,560
[SPEAKER_00] Postaješ hladan i dobijaš one osjećaj.

52
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,899
[SPEAKER_00] Šta će meni Bog?

53
00:06:53,740 --> 00:06:56,439
[SPEAKER_00] I čovjek koji odabra ovaj materijalni svijet

54
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:58,740
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo što ovaj svijet nudi,

55
00:06:58,740 --> 00:07:02,100
[SPEAKER_00] on ne čuje poziv Isusov.

56
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:04,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dođi i slijedi me.

57
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:08,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ako hoćeš, odreci se svega.

58
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:08,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

59
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:13,699
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo puno onih danas u svijetu

60
00:07:13,699 --> 00:07:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] koji su puni sebe.

61
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,439
[SPEAKER_00] Koji se pokazuju.

62
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:18,879
[SPEAKER_00] Koji se dokazuju.

63
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:20,839
[SPEAKER_00] Koji nema šanse

64
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:22,759
[SPEAKER_00] da bi se ponizili.

65
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:24,959
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi priznali svoju gresnost.

66
00:07:24,959 --> 00:07:27,180
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi priznali svoju slabost.

67
00:07:27,180 --> 00:07:29,720
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su kao pod navodnicima

68
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek jaki

69
00:07:31,579 --> 00:07:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] pred drugima.

70
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:36,319
[SPEAKER_00] A u svojim vlastitim sobama plaću.

71
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:38,079
[SPEAKER_00] Nezadovoljni

72
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:40,660
[SPEAKER_00] jer im savjest ubija

73
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] takav način života i grijeh

74
00:07:43,019 --> 00:07:44,699
[SPEAKER_00] u vlastitom životu.

75
00:07:44,699 --> 00:07:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog poštuje.

76
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,759
[SPEAKER_00] Danas pred tebe stavljam

77
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] život ili smrt.

78
00:07:50,839 --> 00:07:51,680
[SPEAKER_00] biraj.

79
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,379
[SPEAKER_00] Samo

80
00:07:53,379 --> 00:07:56,879
[SPEAKER_00] oni koji su krenuli ovim svijetom

81
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:57,899
[SPEAKER_00] vođeni

82
00:07:57,899 --> 00:08:01,060
[SPEAKER_00] zaboravljaju jednu stvar.

83
00:08:01,060 --> 00:08:03,399
[SPEAKER_00] Da je Bog stvorio

84
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] i materialno dobro

85
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] i stvari

86
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] i sve u ovom svijetu

87
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:08,660
[SPEAKER_00] u službi čovjeka.

88
00:08:08,660 --> 00:08:11,160
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je tužno

89
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,879
[SPEAKER_00] kada čovjek postane

90
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] instrument tih stvari.

91
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] umjesto da on upravlja stvarima

92
00:08:17,139 --> 00:08:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] i materialnim

93
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] i svim što ima

94
00:08:19,220 --> 00:08:20,339
[SPEAKER_00] kad te stvari

95
00:08:20,339 --> 00:08:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] počinju upravljati njim.

96
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] Možete zamisliti

97
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,220
[SPEAKER_00] kad takve osobe

98
00:08:25,220 --> 00:08:26,639
[SPEAKER_00] ne osjećaju ljubav Božiju

99
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:29,259
[SPEAKER_00] i kad se ostaneš

100
00:08:29,259 --> 00:08:30,120
[SPEAKER_00] sam u sobi.

101
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,700
[SPEAKER_00] Koja boli.

102
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] Koja tuga.

103
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:36,820
[SPEAKER_00] Koji jav, čemer.

104
00:08:36,820 --> 00:08:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] Kad znaš da te iskreno

105
00:08:39,059 --> 00:08:39,740
[SPEAKER_00] i prijatelje

106
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:40,740
[SPEAKER_00] s kojima se okruža

107
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:41,299
[SPEAKER_00] ne ljube.

108
00:08:41,299 --> 00:08:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] Jer te ljube

109
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:44,320
[SPEAKER_00] zbog koristi.

110
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] A koliko je onda

111
00:08:48,039 --> 00:08:49,720
[SPEAKER_00] teško krenuti naprijed.

112
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] I sada ću vam reći

113
00:08:52,159 --> 00:08:54,379
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ovo govorim.

114
00:08:54,379 --> 00:08:55,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj uvod.

115
00:08:55,700 --> 00:08:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] Mi

116
00:08:58,279 --> 00:09:00,620
[SPEAKER_00] kao da se zadovoljimo

117
00:09:00,620 --> 00:09:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] minimumom

118
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] ponekad ispovjed

119
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,340
[SPEAKER_00] ponekad pokajanje

120
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:08,799
[SPEAKER_00] ponekad neka molitva

121
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:09,240
[SPEAKER_00] više

122
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] i to je to.

123
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] je li to dovoljno

124
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,399
[SPEAKER_00] za jednog kršćanina?

125
00:09:14,399 --> 00:09:15,460
[SPEAKER_00] Nije.

126
00:09:15,460 --> 00:09:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

127
00:09:18,019 --> 00:09:19,600
[SPEAKER_00] sveta Katarina Sijenska

128
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,519
[SPEAKER_00] i mnogi drugi sveci

129
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:23,379
[SPEAKER_00] govore o jednom

130
00:09:23,379 --> 00:09:24,740
[SPEAKER_00] duhovnom putovanju.

131
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:27,259
[SPEAKER_00] A što je korizma

132
00:09:27,259 --> 00:09:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] nego putovanje?

133
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ring.

134
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:30,519
[SPEAKER_00] Mi u korizmu

135
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,799
[SPEAKER_00] ulazimo u duhovni ring

136
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:33,399
[SPEAKER_00] gdje se borimo

137
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] i protiv sebe samih,

138
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:36,919
[SPEAKER_00] protiv džavla.

139
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] Sveta Katarina Sijenska

140
00:09:39,940 --> 00:09:40,860
[SPEAKER_00] i mnogi drugi sveci

141
00:09:40,860 --> 00:09:42,299
[SPEAKER_00] govore o tom duhovnom putovanju

142
00:09:42,940 --> 00:09:44,759
[SPEAKER_00] o razlišitim etapama

143
00:09:44,759 --> 00:09:45,759
[SPEAKER_00] duhovnosti,

144
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] ma ne duhovnosti,

145
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] da razumijete,

146
00:09:48,019 --> 00:09:51,399
[SPEAKER_00] nego o razlišitim etapama

147
00:09:51,399 --> 00:09:53,700
[SPEAKER_00] naše ljubavi prema Bogu.

148
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:55,759
[SPEAKER_00] I ova propoljeda

149
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] će vas biti

150
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:57,740
[SPEAKER_00] najbitnija stvar

151
00:09:57,740 --> 00:09:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] da shvatite.

152
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:01,779
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je tvoja ljubav

153
00:10:01,779 --> 00:10:03,440
[SPEAKER_00] danas prema Bogu?

154
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,419
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi ti već

155
00:10:05,419 --> 00:10:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] 50, 60 godina,

156
00:10:07,059 --> 00:10:08,259
[SPEAKER_00] imaš 80,

157
00:10:08,259 --> 00:10:09,820
[SPEAKER_00] a ti si uvijek

158
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:11,100
[SPEAKER_00] u startnoj poziciji.

159
00:10:11,100 --> 00:10:13,799
[SPEAKER_00] Što nije u redu s nama?

160
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] Što mi to ne razumijemo

161
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:17,179
[SPEAKER_00] u vjeri

162
00:10:17,179 --> 00:10:19,120
[SPEAKER_00] da smo mi stalno

163
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,840
[SPEAKER_00] na početku?

164
00:10:24,179 --> 00:10:26,139
[SPEAKER_00] I sveta Katarina

165
00:10:26,139 --> 00:10:26,899
[SPEAKER_00] i naravno,

166
00:10:26,899 --> 00:10:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] kažem,

167
00:10:27,679 --> 00:10:28,799
[SPEAKER_00] mnogi drugi sveci

168
00:10:28,799 --> 00:10:31,200
[SPEAKER_00] i sveti Bernardin

169
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] i ostali govore

170
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:35,740
[SPEAKER_00] o putu čišćenja,

171
00:10:35,740 --> 00:10:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] o putu prosvjetljenja,

172
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,059
[SPEAKER_00] o putu sjedinjenja

173
00:10:40,059 --> 00:10:41,440
[SPEAKER_00] s Bogom.

174
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:44,799
[SPEAKER_00] Vi često puta mislite

175
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] kao i mnogi kršani,

176
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,820
[SPEAKER_00] pa krećujemo od sebe

177
00:10:47,820 --> 00:10:48,700
[SPEAKER_00] kao svečenika.

178
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:51,419
[SPEAKER_00] Pitam te,

179
00:10:51,419 --> 00:10:52,899
[SPEAKER_00] na koje si ti razini sada?

180
00:10:52,899 --> 00:10:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi u fazi čišćenja,

181
00:10:55,779 --> 00:10:57,580
[SPEAKER_00] prosvjetljenja

182
00:10:57,580 --> 00:10:59,200
[SPEAKER_00] ili si već sjedinjen

183
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] toliko čisto

184
00:11:00,019 --> 00:11:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] s Bogom

185
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] da se razumiš?

186
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:03,879
[SPEAKER_00] Ali idemo obrazlošiti

187
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:04,639
[SPEAKER_00] jedno po jedno.

188
00:11:07,899 --> 00:11:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] puno puta

189
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] samo ponavljamo

190
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:12,039
